Add a visible test banner near the top of the page:

<style>
  .test-banner {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1px solid #facc15;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #422006;
    color: #fef3c7;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>

<div class="test-banner" role="status">Test banner</div>
